text: Lycaneptia nigrobasalis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Tippmann in 1960. It is known from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Lycaneptia nigrobasalis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1960
